					&lt;p&gt;It is certainly possible to make a smoked beer by using a smoked malt at the brewing stage. Excellent information here: &lt;a href="http://byo.com/pilsner/item/306-brewing-smoked-beers-tips-from-the-pros" rel="nofollow"&gt;Brewing Smoked Beers: Tips from the Pros.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

