				<Text Type="text">
					&lt;p&gt;Peated malt can provide a beer with subtle smokiness. Peated malt is malt that has been smoked over peat (decaying vegetation). This is common in Scotch &amp;amp; Whisky Ales. 
					Cheers&lt;/p&gt;

				</Text>
