				<Text Type="text">
					&lt;p&gt;One other potential source of smoke flavors is actually the yeast.  Some yeast produce phenolic compounds during fermentation that produce smoke flavors and aromas.  Scottish yeast strains in particular are known for this.&lt;/p&gt;

				</Text>
